{"abstract":[{"text":"Registers a WhatsApp number for WhatsApp Business messaging.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/registerwhatsappnumber:"]}],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"registerWhatsappNumber:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","text":"NSString"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"number","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"number","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The phone number in E.164 international format."}]}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Associates a WhatsApp number with the current device for WhatsApp Business API","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"messaging campaigns. This enables rich messaging with images, documents, and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"interactive buttons through WhatsApp."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The phone number must be in E.164 international format:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Start with ‘+’ followed by country code"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"No spaces, dashes, or parentheses","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Must be a valid WhatsApp-enabled number","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"anchor":"Example","type":"heading","text":"Example","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Register WhatsApp during communication preferences setup:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class CommunicationPreferencesManager {","","    struct Preferences {","        var pushEnabled: Bool","        var smsEnabled: Bool","        var whatsappEnabled: Bool","        var whatsappNumber: String?","    }","","    func savePreferences(_ preferences: Preferences) {","        \/\/ Register WhatsApp if user opted in and provided number","        if preferences.whatsappEnabled, let number = preferences.whatsappNumber {","            let normalizedNumber = normalizePhoneNumber(number)","            Pushwoosh.configure.registerWhatsappNumber(normalizedNumber)","        }","","        \/\/ Update channel preferences tags","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","            \"channel_push\": preferences.pushEnabled,","            \"channel_sms\": preferences.smsEnabled,","            \"channel_whatsapp\": preferences.whatsappEnabled","        ])","    }","","    private func normalizePhoneNumber(_ phone: String) -> String {","        let digits = phone.filter { $0.isNumber }","        return phone.hasPrefix(\"+\") ? \"+\\(digits)\" : \"+\\(digits)\"","    }","}"]}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)registerWhatsappNumber:","roleHeading":"Type Method","title":"registerWhatsappNumber:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"registerWhatsappNumber:","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"registerWhatsappNumber:","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"method"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/registerWhatsappNumber:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/registerWhatsappNumber:":{"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"registerWhatsappNumber:","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/registerWhatsappNumber:","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/registerwhatsappnumber:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"registerWhatsappNumber:"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Registers a WhatsApp number for WhatsApp Business messaging.","type":"text"}],"title":"registerWhatsappNumber:","kind":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","title":"PWConfiguration","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK.","type":"text"}],"title":"PushwooshCore","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore"}}}